Mipa key duh tan hetah : https://www.youtube.com/watch?reload=9&v=WTis2s2qsSI
Phuahtu :  Bd-a
Music : C Lalhmuaka, 3 Sister youtube channel.

Lyrics
Aw ka nun khawhar chau tak hian,
Hmangaihtu a ngai thin a;
Aw ka nunna hian Lalpa a ngai a ni.

I tello chuan nun a kim lo,
Ka zinkawng khawhar ah hian;
An sawi nin loh ramnuam El Dorado,
An ngai thin ang hian,
Lalpa ka ngai em che.

Aw ka nun chau rethei tak hian,
Hnemtu a ngai a ni;
Aw ka hringnun hian Lalpa a ngai a ni.

Hmangaihtu tawnglo nun khawhar,
Kei misual leh rethei tan hian;
Aw lo eng ang che ka nun khawhar ah hian.
